    "translation":{"eng":"If you bind Śrī Gaurāṅga, the king of the brāhmaṇas and the best of dancers, within your heart, then what will material existence and death be able to do to you? Narottama dāsa says, “There is no one equal to Śrī Gaurāṅga. Even without being worshiped, He bestows the treasure of prema.”"}}
